Step 1: Final Answer

Based on the search results, three travel credit cards that offer no foreign transaction fees, 2x or more points on travel purchases, and a sign-up bonus of at least 50,000 points are:

1. Chase Sapphire Preferred® Card
   - No foreign transaction fees
   - 5x points on travel purchased through Chase Ultimate Rewards®
   - 2x points on other travel purchases
   - 60,000 bonus points after spending $4,000 in the first 3 months

2. Capital One Venture Rewards Credit Card
   - No foreign transaction fees
   - 2x miles on every purchase
   - 5x miles on hotels and rental cars booked through Capital One Travel
   - 75,000 miles bonus after spending $4,000 in the first 3 months

3. Capital One Venture X Rewards Credit Card
   - No foreign transaction fees
   - 2x miles on all purchases
   - 10x miles on hotels and rental cars booked through Capital One Travel
   - 5x miles on flights booked through Capital One Travel
   - 75,000 miles bonus after spending $4,000 in the first 3 months

These cards offer excellent rewards for travelers, with no foreign transaction fees and substantial sign-up bonuses. The Chase Sapphire Preferred® has a lower annual fee of $95, while the Capital One Venture cards have higher annual fees but offer more premium benefits.

